00:06:43.339 --> 00:06:45.339
Jehovah keeps blessing me.

00:06:45.339 --> 00:06:53.339
In one of the blessings, I got a letter for the school for Kingdom Evangelises.

00:06:53.339 --> 00:06:59.339
It is like Jehovah is telling me, I want you to continue.

